{"id":"grizzled","term":"Grizzled","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Party-coloured, as goats (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:10\">Gen. 31:10</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 31:12\">12</a>), horses (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 6:3\">Zech. 6:3</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 6:6\">6</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 31:10","Genesis 31:12","Zechariah 6:3","Zechariah 6:6"]}